org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api

Interface IPageView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPageView, AbstractPageViewProxy, PageView, PageViewProxy

    public interface IPageView
extends com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto

    A data-access layer data-transfer-object interface for the PageView. The data-transfer-object class and proxy class implement this interface, as does the business-layer data-transfer-object class.

    A single access of a URI for a given IP address at a given date and time; may be part of a session if it has a session id

    Stereotypes:

    • Persistent
    • SequenceKey

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
